y (array of strings noting interactions or contraindications considering current medications and allergies; empty array if none identified), follow_up_questions (array of strings: additional history, examination, or vitals to obtain to narrow the differential), allergy_alerts (array of strings), red_flags (array of strings), icd10_suggestions (array of objects each with code and description).\" }, { role: \"user\", content: \"CONTEXT: \" + ($json.context_json || \"{}\") + \"\\n\\nBULLETS:\\n\" + ($json.bullets || \"\") + \"\\n\\nReturn the professional SOAP note and decision support as a JSON object now.\" } ] }) }}",
